Package: ICV
Title: Indirect cross-validation (ICV) for kernel density estimation
Version: 0.1.2017
Author: Olga Savchuk
Maintainer: Olga Savchuk <olga.y.savchuk@gmail.com>
Description: Functions for computing the global and local Gaussian density estimates based on the ICV bandwidth. See the article of Savchuk, O.Y., Hart, J.D., Sheather, S.J. (2010). Indirect cross-validation for density estimation. Journal of the American Statistical Association, 105(489), 415-423.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.1)
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1